om: 0px;"><span style="font-weight: bolder;">老子的顺乎自然，怡淡寡欲，静养柔气等养生观点。两千多年来不仅一直成为道家养生的指导思想，而且被我国传统医学所接受，后经历代医家和养生学家的不断补充、提高，逐发展成为我国独特的中医养生之道 。</span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(175, 193, 224);"><section style="position: static;"><section style="text-align: left;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><br/></p></section></section></section><section style="text-align: center; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(175, 193, 224); position: static;"><section style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; position: static;"><section style="display: inline-block; width: 611.161px; vertical-align: top;"><section style="position: static;"><section style="margin-bottom: -1px; text-align: left; transform: translate3d(2px, 0px, 0px); position: static;"><section style="padding-right: 10px; padding-left: 10px; display: inline-block; min-width: 10%; max-width: 100%; vertical-align: top; border-width: 1px; border-radius: 8px 8px 0px 0px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(255, 177, 0); background-color: rgb(249, 110, 87);"><section><section style="position: static;"><section style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2; letter-spacing: 2px;"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;">主讲名师</p></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="position: static;"><section style="position: static;"><section style="padding: 10px; display: inline-block; width: 605.045px; vertical-align: top; border-color: rgb(249, 110, 87); border-width: 3px; border-radius: 0px 8px 8px; border-style: solid; overflow: hidden;"><section style="position: static;"><section style="margin-bottom: 10px; position: static;"><section style="max-width: 100%; vertical-align: middle; display: inline-block; line-height: 0;"><img class="raw-image" src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appAWL1qqau1296/image/uedi